snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild - Expansion Pass: DLC Pack EX The Bells’ Arietta Trailer
snippet.description:
The Sheikah Bell, located in the newly discovered Flo Ohneh Shrine, holds unbelievable powers such as to reverse time itself. You must rise today. The last installment of The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild Expansion Pass: The Bells' Arietta is nearly around the corner. The exhilarating adventure comes to a dramatic finale in Fall 2018!

#NintendoSwitch #LegendofZelda #BreathoftheWild #e32018
